爱莎贝儿-140CM-M 粉肤 RAD041 蝶野未梦Chono Miyu-喜欢今日的惊喜吗？
“出差辛苦了……”
她声音软得像化开的蜜，踮脚贴上来，
指尖沿着我衬衫纽扣一路向下，
“所以……特意准备了这个惊喜。”

热气喷在我耳边，她踮着脚尖蹭了蹭，
细绳在肌肤上勒出浅浅红痕。我再也忍不了，
低头狠狠吻下去，
手掌直接覆上那几乎不存在的布料，
指腹碾过最敏感的一点。

她轻哼一声，身体软软塌进我怀里。
“今晚……不许睡哦。”她含着我的耳垂，
气息发颤，“人家可是忍了好几天呢。”
身型：140CM-M 粉肤

Elsa Babe-140CM-M Pink RAD041 Chono Miyu-Did you like today's surprise?
"You must be tired from your business trip..."
Her voice was as soft as melting honey as she tiptoed closer,
her fingertips tracing the buttons of my shirt downwards,
"So... I specially prepared this surprise."

Her breath warm against my ear, she tiptoed and rubbed against me,
the thin string leaving faint red marks on my skin. I couldn't hold back any longer,
I lowered my head and kissed her fiercely,
my palm directly covering the almost non-existent fabric,
my fingertips rubbing against the most sensitive spot.

She let out a soft moan, her body slumping softly into my arms.
"Tonight... you're not allowed to sleep, okay?" she whispered in my earlobe,
her breath trembling, "I've been holding back for days."
Body type: 140CM-M with Pink skin tone.
